<p><strong>Pro tip:</strong> The most dangerous red flag is a combination of unrealistic expectations plus multiple fired agencies. This client has learned that firing agencies is easier than adjusting expectations. Your questionnaire should surface this pattern before you invest strategy hours.</p>
